W. H. Bethea, as Tax Assessor for Taylor County, Plaintiff in Error, v. State ex rel. Taylor County Lumber Company, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Taylor. Van G. Swearingen, Attorney General, for Plaintiff in Error; TV. B. Davis, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of the Attorney General.
